The '''2014 Spanish motorcycle Grand Prix''' was the fourth round of the [[2014 Grand Prix motorcycle racing season|2014 MotoGP season]]. It was held at the [[Circuito de Jerez]] in [[Jerez de la Frontera]] on 4 May 2014.

